    <step order="4">Verify the call still goes through `authenticatedFetch` from `@spaarke/auth` (no Bearer literals introduced). Confirm no `accessToken` prop drilling.</step>
    <step order="5">Add unit tests for the request body shape: (a) with `searchIndexName="spaarke-file-index"` â†’ body includes the field with that value; (b) with `searchIndexName=""` â†’ body does NOT include the field; (c) with `searchIndexName` omitted â†’ body does NOT include the field. Mock the `authenticatedFetch` to inspect the body argument.</step>
